---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const url = new URL(Astro.request.url);
const section = url.searchParams.get("section") || "This section";
---

<Layout title={`${section} | Knit it Now`}>

<section class="container" style="max-width:820px; margin:60px auto;">

<h1>{section} is being built</h1>

<p class="intro intro-accent">
We're currently building this area to include clear guides, helpful tools, and practical examples for machine knitters.
</p>

<p>
Rather than rushing something unfinished, we're taking the time to make sure this section is genuinely useful.
</p>

<p>
Check back soon — new resources are being added regularly.
</p>

<hr>

<p><strong>In the meantime:</strong></p>

<ul>
<li><a href="/videos">Explore the Video Library</a></li>
<li><a href="/troubleshoot">Visit the Troubleshooting Guide</a></li>
<li><a href="/learn/reference">Browse the Reference pages</a></li>
</ul>

</section>

</Layout>